info.description: Logicdrop Sparks API and Python Client.  Logicdrop Sparks lets users build rules, analyze data, and automate documents.  Use it to make decisions faster, generate documents better, and learn from your data.  ### Documentation - [User Documentation](https://docs.logicdrop.com)  ### Modules - [Sparks Compute](https://docs.logicdrop.com/rules/introduction) - [Sparks Decision Tables](https://docs.logicdrop.com/rules/authoring-decision-tables) - [Sparks Documents](https://docs.logicdrop.com/documents/introduction)  ### Clients - [OpenAPI Clients](https://docs.logicdrop.com/development/sample-clients)  ### Security - [Authorizing API Requests](https://docs.logicdrop.com/development/authorization)   # noqa: E501
